  <!-- NEW AUTHORITY CALLOUT -->
  <section class="new-authority-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="na-content">
        <div class="na-badge">For New Authorities</div>
        <h2>Just Got Your DOT?<br/><span class="gold">We've Got You.</span></h2>
        <p>Getting insurance for a new authority is different. Most agents don't explain the process - they just send you a bill. We walk you through every coverage, every requirement, every step.</p>
        <a href="/new-authorities" class="btn-outline-dark">Learn What You Actually Need &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY RMS -->
  <section class="values">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="values-header">
        <span class="section-num">01</span>
        <h2>The Industry Profits From Your Confusion.<br/><span class="gold">We Don't.</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="value-columns">
        <div class="value-col">
          <h3>We Actually Explain Things</h3>
          <p>Insurance should make sense to you. If your agent can't explain it clearly, they either don't understand it or don't want you to.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-col">
          <h3>We Know Your Business First</h3>
          <p>We ask what you haul, where you go, how you run. Then we find coverage that actually fits. Not maximum coverage. Right coverage.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-col">
          <h3>When You Call, Things Happen</h3>
          <p>You say what you need, it happens. Certificate requests get done while you're on the phone. One moment... done.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE COVER -->
  <section class="coverage">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header-centered">
        <span class="section-tag">Coverage</span>
        <h2>Commercial Trucking Insurance<br/>That Actually <span class="gold">Makes Sense</span></h2>
        <p class="section-intro">We specialize in commercial trucking insurance for owner-operators and small fleets. Every coverage we offer, we can explain in plain English. If we can't explain why you need it, you probably don't.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="coverage-grid">
        <div class="coverage-card">
          <div class="coverage-badge required">Required by FMCSA</div>
          <h3>Auto Liability</h3>
          <p>The coverage that keeps you legal. Protects you when you're at fault in an accident. Federal law requires $750,000 minimum for interstate carriers—some brokers and shippers require $1 million. We'll help you understand what limits you actually need.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="coverage-card">
          <div class="coverage-badge">Protect Your Truck</div>
          <h3>Physical Damage</h3>
          <p>Covers your rig if it's damaged or totaled—collision, fire, theft, vandalism. This is the coverage that lets you sleep at night. Comprehensive and collision, explained without the jargon.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="coverage-card">
          <div class="coverage-badge">Protect What You Haul</div>
          <h3>Cargo Insurance</h3>
          <p>Covers the freight you're hauling if it's damaged, stolen, or lost. Required by most brokers and shippers. Limits depend on what you haul—$100K is common, some commodities need more.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="coverage-card">
          <div class="coverage-badge">Slip and Fall Coverage</div>
          <h3>General Liability</h3>
          <p>Protects your business when you're not in the truck—loading docks, customer locations, your office. Not required by law, but smart if you're ever on foot at a customer site.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="coverage-card">
          <div class="coverage-badge">Off-Dispatch Coverage</div>
          <h3>Non-Trucking Liability</h3>
          <p>Covers you when you're driving but not under dispatch—heading home, running errands in the truck, bobtailing to pick up a trailer. Fills the gap your motor carrier's policy doesn't cover.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="coverage-card">
          <div class="coverage-badge">Your Safety Net</div>
          <h3>Occupational Accident</h3>
          <p>Medical coverage and disability protection if you're injured on the job. For owner-operators who aren't covered by workers' comp. Pays medical bills and lost income when you can't drive.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO WE HELP -->
  <section class="who-we-help">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header-left">
        <span class="section-tag">Who We Serve</span>
        <h2>Built for Truckers.<br/><span class="gold">Only Truckers.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-intro">We don't do home insurance. We don't do life insurance. We don't dabble in trucking on the side. This is all we do—which means we actually know what we're talking about.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="customer-grid">
        <div class="customer-card">
          <div class="customer-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"/>
              <polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"/>
              <circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/>
              <circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="customer-type">1-3 Trucks</span>
          <h3>Owner-Operators</h3>
          <p>You own your truck. You run your business. You need an agent who understands that every dollar matters and every minute on hold is money lost. We get it—we work with hundreds of owner-operators just like you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-card">
          <div class="customer-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="customer-type">Just Got Your MC/DOT?</span>
          <h3>New Authorities</h3>
          <p>Starting a trucking company is complicated enough without insurance confusion. We specialize in new authorities—we know the FMCSA requirements, the filing deadlines, and how to get you covered fast so you can start hauling.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-card">
          <div class="customer-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="customer-type">3-10 Trucks</span>
          <h3>Small Fleets</h3>
          <p>Growing your fleet means growing your coverage. We help small fleets scale their insurance without the corporate runaround. Same fast service, same straight answers, just bigger policies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-card">
          <div class="customer-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/>
              <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="customer-type">Hotshot • General Freight • Towing • Box Trucks</span>
          <h3>Specific Operations</h3>
          <p>Different operations need different coverage. We ask what you haul, where you go, how you run—then we match coverage to your actual business, not some generic template.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="process">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="process-header">
        <span class="section-num">02</span>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">01</span>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Tell Us About Your Operation</h4>
            <p>Quick call or form. We ask the right questions so you don't have to guess what we need.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">02</span>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Get Options That Fit</h4>
            <p>We shop the same carriers everyone uses, but we explain what you're actually buying.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">03</span>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Stay Covered, Stay Moving</h4>
            <p>Certs when you need them. Answers when you have questions. We're here.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="testimonials">
